#. <section class="sutta" id="mn67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn67:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 67"
msgstr "Middle Discourses 67"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn67:0.2"
msgid "Cātumasutta"
msgstr "At Cātumā"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.457"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "mn67:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā cātumāyaṃ viharati āmalakīvane."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Cātumā in a myrobalan grove."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya2"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena sāriputtamoggallānappamukhāni pañcamattāni "
"bhikkhusatāni cātumaṃ anuppattāni honti bhagavantaṃ dassanāya."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time around five hundred mendicants headed by Sāriputta and "
"Moggallāna arrived at Cātumā to see the Buddha."

msgctxt "mn67:2.2"
msgid ""
"Te ca āgantukā bhikkhū nevāsikehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ paṭisammodamānā "
"senāsanāni paññāpayamānā pattacīvarāni paṭisāmayamānā uccāsaddā mahāsaddā "
"ahesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"And the visiting mendicants, while exchanging pleasantries with the resident "
"mendicants, preparing their lodgings, and putting away their bowls and "
"robes, made a dreadful racket."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya3"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Ānanda:"

msgctxt "mn67:3.2"
msgid "“ke panete, ānanda, uccāsaddā mahāsaddā, kevaṭṭā maññe macchavilope”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, who’s making that dreadful racket? You’d think it was fishermen "
"hauling in a catch!”"

msgctxt "mn67:3.3"
msgid ""
"“Etāni, bhante, sāriputtamoggallānappamukhāni pañcamattāni bhikkhusatāni "
"cātumaṃ anuppattāni bhagavantaṃ dassanāya."
msgstr "And Ānanda told him what had happened."

msgctxt "mn67:3.4"
msgid ""
"Te āgantukā bhikkhū nevāsikehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ paṭisammodamānā senāsanāni "
"paññāpayamānā pattacīvarāni paṭisāmayamānā uccāsaddā mahāsaddā”ti. "
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya4"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:4.1"
msgid "“Tenahānanda, mama vacanena te bhikkhū āmantehi:"
msgstr "“Well then, Ānanda, in my name tell those mendicants that"

msgctxt "mn67:4.2"
msgid "‘satthā āyasmante āmantetī’”ti."
msgstr "the teacher summons them.”"

msgctxt "mn67:4.3"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho āyasmā ānando bhagavato paṭissutvā yena te bhikkhū "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā te bhikkhū etadavoca:"
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” Ānanda replied. He went to those mendicants and said:"

msgctxt "mn67:4.4"
msgid "“satthā āyasmante āmantetī”ti."
msgstr "“Venerables, the teacher summons you.”"

msgctxt "mn67:4.5"
msgid ""
"“Evamāvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato ānandassa paṭissutvā yena bhagavā "
"tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. "
"Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te bhikkhū bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Yes, reverend,” replied those mendicants. Then they rose from their seats "
"and went to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to "
"them:"

msgctxt "mn67:4.6"
msgid ""
"“kiṃ nu tumhe, bhikkhave, uccāsaddā mahāsaddā, kevaṭṭā maññe macchavilope”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, what’s with that dreadful racket? You’d think it was fishermen "
"hauling in a catch!”"

msgctxt "mn67:4.7"
msgid ""
"“Imāni, bhante, sāriputtamoggallānappamukhāni pañcamattāni bhikkhusatāni "
"cātumaṃ anuppattāni bhagavantaṃ dassanāya."
msgstr "And they told him what had happened."

msgctxt "mn67:4.8"
msgid ""
"Teme āgantukā bhikkhū nevāsikehi bhikkhūhi saddhiṃ paṭisammodamānā "
"senāsanāni paññāpayamānā pattacīvarāni paṭisāmayamānā uccāsaddā mahāsaddā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya5"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:5.1"
msgid "“Gacchatha, bhikkhave, paṇāmemi vo, na vo mama santike vatthabban”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Go away, mendicants, I dismiss you. You are not to stay in my presence.”"

msgctxt "mn67:5.2"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paṭissutvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā senāsanaṃ saṃsāmetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"pakkamiṃsu."
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied those mendicants. They got up from their seats, bowed, "
"and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on their right. They set "
"their lodgings in order and left, taking their bowls and robes."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya6"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.458"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: santhāgāre → sandhāgāre (mr)
msgctxt "mn67:6.1"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena cātumeyyakā sakyā santhāgāre sannipatitā honti "
"kenacideva karaṇīyena."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the Sakyans of Cātumā were sitting together at the meeting "
"hall on some business."

msgctxt "mn67:6.2"
msgid "Addasaṃsu kho cātumeyyakā sakyā te bhikkhū dūratova āgacchante;"
msgstr "Seeing those mendicants coming off in the distance,"

msgctxt "mn67:6.3"
msgid ""
"disvāna yena te bhikkhū tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā te bhikkhū "
"etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr "they went up to them and said:"

msgctxt "mn67:6.4"
msgid "“handa kahaṃ pana tumhe āyasmanto gacchathā”ti?"
msgstr "“Hello venerables, where are you going?”"

msgctxt "mn67:6.5"
msgid "“Bhagavatā kho, āvuso, bhikkhusaṃgho paṇāmito”ti."
msgstr "“Sirs, the mendicant Saṅgha has been dismissed by the Buddha.”"

msgctxt "mn67:6.6"
msgid ""
"“Tenahāyasmanto muhuttaṃ nisīdatha, appeva nāma mayaṃ sakkuṇeyyāma "
"bhagavantaṃ pasādetun”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Well then, venerables, sit here for a minute. Hopefully we’ll be able to "
"restore the Buddha’s confidence.”"

msgctxt "mn67:6.7"
msgid "“Evamāvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū cātumeyyakānaṃ sakyānaṃ paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sirs,” replied the mendicants."

#. <a class="nya" id="nya7"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:7.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho cātumeyyakā sakyā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho "
"cātumeyyakā sakyā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Sakyans of Cātumā went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one "
"side, and said to him:"

msgctxt "mn67:7.2"
msgid "“abhinandatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ;"
msgstr "“May the Buddha approve of the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:7.3"
msgid "abhivadatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ."
msgstr "May the Buddha welcome the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:7.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, bhagavatā pubbe bhikkhusaṃgho anuggahito; evameva "
"bhagavā etarahi anuggaṇhātu bhikkhusaṃghaṃ."
msgstr "May the Buddha support the mendicant Saṅgha now as he did in the past!"

msgctxt "mn67:7.5"
msgid ""
"Santettha, bhante, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ dhammavinayaṃ."
msgstr ""
"There are mendicants here who are junior, recently gone forth, newly come to "
"this teaching and training."

msgctxt "mn67:7.6"
msgid ""
"Tesaṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, siyā vipariṇāmo."
msgstr "If they don’t get to see the Buddha they may change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:7.7"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, bījānaṃ taruṇānaṃ udakaṃ alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ "
"siyā vipariṇāmo;"
msgstr "If young seedlings don’t get water they may change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:7.8"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhante, santettha bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, tesaṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, "
"siyā vipariṇāmo."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, there are mendicants here who are junior, recently gone "
"forth, newly come to this teaching and training. If they don’t get to see "
"the Buddha they may change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:7.9"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, vacchassa taruṇassa mātaraṃ apassantassa siyā "
"aññathattaṃ, siyā vipariṇāmo;"
msgstr "If a young calf doesn’t see its mother it may change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:7.10"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhante, santettha bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, tesaṃ bhagavantaṃ apassantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, siyā "
"vipariṇāmo."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, there are mendicants here who are junior, recently gone "
"forth, newly come to this teaching and training. If they don’t get to see "
"the Buddha they may change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:7.11"
msgid "Abhinandatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ;"
msgstr "May the Buddha approve of the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:7.12"
msgid "abhivadatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ."
msgstr "May the Buddha welcome the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:7.13"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, bhagavatā pubbe bhikkhusaṃgho anuggahito; evameva "
"bhagavā etarahi anuggaṇhātu bhikkhusaṃghan”ti."
msgstr "May the Buddha support the mendicant Saṅgha now as he did in the past!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.459"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: samiñjitaṃ → sammiñjitaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn67:8.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brahmā sahampati bhagavato cetasā cetoparivitakkamaññāya—seyyathāpi "
"nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ pasāreyya, pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ "
"samiñjeyya; evameva—brahmaloke antarahito bhagavato purato pāturahosi."
msgstr ""
"Then Brahmā Sahampati knew what the Buddha was thinking. As easily as a "
"strong person would extend or contract their arm, he vanished from the "
"Brahmā realm and reappeared in front of the Buddha."

msgctxt "mn67:8.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brahmā sahampati ekaṃsaṃ uttarāsaṅgaṃ karitvā yena bhagavā "
"tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"He arranged his robe over one shoulder, raised his joined palms toward the "
"Buddha, and said:"

#. <a class="nya" id="nya9"></a>
msgctxt "mn67:9.1"
msgid "“abhinandatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ;"
msgstr "“May the Buddha approve of the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:9.2"
msgid "abhivadatu, bhante, bhagavā bhikkhusaṃghaṃ."
msgstr "May the Buddha welcome the mendicant Saṅgha!"

msgctxt "mn67:9.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, bhagavatā pubbe bhikkhusaṃgho anuggahito; evameva "
"bhagavā etarahi anuggaṇhātu bhikkhusaṃghaṃ."
msgstr "May the Buddha support the mendicant Saṅgha now as he did in the past!"

