msgid ""
"Santettha, bhante, bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, tesaṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, "
"siyā vipariṇāmo."
msgstr ""
