"change and fall apart."

msgctxt "mn67:9.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhante, bījānaṃ taruṇānaṃ udakaṃ alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, "
"siyā vipariṇāmo;"
msgstr "If young seedlings don’t get water they may change and fall apart. …"

msgctxt "mn67:9.6"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhante, santettha bhikkhū navā acirapabbajitā adhunāgatā imaṃ "
"dhammavinayaṃ, tesaṃ bhagavantaṃ dassanāya alabhantānaṃ siyā aññathattaṃ, "
"siyā vipariṇāmo."
msgstr ""

